title: My 4 Scans - February 2014 (gnv64)
description:
I have been scanning some books over past few weeks. Here I am sharing 4 of them with you. All books are in PDF format with OCR, bookmarks & covers:

1. Classic Horror Stories 7 mb
2. Conversations with a Spirit 9 mb
3. Konkani Folk Tales 7.75 mb
4. World's Most Loved Short Stories 6.75 mb

I have also included a sample of my forthcoming scan to know if you are interested!
